<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Sign Up Successful - HoH Bank</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <style>
    body {
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 10%, #232946 0%, #0f172a 100%);
      color: #7df9ff;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 5rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #181f36;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px #22c55e22;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #22c55e;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #22c55e;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .login-btn {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e 0%, #7df9ff 100%);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #10182a;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #22c55e33;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .login-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7df9ff 0%, #22c55e 100%);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></div>
    <h2>Successfully Signed Up!</h2>
    <p>Your account has been created. Please log in to continue using HoH Bank services.</p>
    <a href="/login/customer" class="login-btn">Go to Login</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
